                    </ul>
                </p>
                <p><a class="btn btn-secondary" href="{{ path('robyulweb_default_commands') }}#gfycat" role="button">Learn more &raquo;</a></p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-12">
                <p>And LastFM (including summary of the lastFM usage on a whole discord) and Translations and osu! and Gallery Mode for Channels and Channel Mirroring Across Servers and Random Pictures from Google Drive folders (timed and on request) and Custom Commands and Spoilers and Reaction polls and <a href="https://cleverbot.com/" target="_blank">Cleverbot</a> and more..</p>
                <p><a class="btn btn-secondary" href="{{ path('robyulweb_default_commands') }}" role="button">View all commands &raquo;</a></p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
